  "about-extrabiblical-writings": "Mayelana nemibhalo engekho eBhayibhelini",
  "apocrypha-info-text": "Akukho mibhalo ekulesi sigaba eyake yabhekwa njengemiBhalo yimiphakathi yamaJuda noma yamaKristu. IBhayibheli liyiqoqo elithile lezincwadi. AmaJuda namaKristu bebelokhu bevumelana ngeTestamente Elidala, elivela eqoqweni eliqinile lemibhalo engcwele abantu bamaJuda abayibiza ngokuthi iTanakh namaKristu ayibiza ngokuthi iTestamente Elidala. Okuqukethwe yiTanakh neTestamente Elidala kufana ncamashi, kodwa kuvame ukuhlelwa ngendlela ehlukile. AmaKristu futhi ayaqaphela iTestamente Elisha, elilandisa indaba kaJesu, izimfundiso zakhe, kanye nemibhalo yabalandeli bakhe. Imibhalo engezansi yayaziwa futhi ifundwa kabanzi ngesikhathi iBhayibheli libhalwa, kodwa ayizange iphathwe njengemiBhalo. Ngenkathi abalobi basendulo ngezinye izikhathi becaphuna imibhalo ehlukahlukene ehlanganisa izimbongi, izazi zefilosofi, kanye neminye imibhalo, ukucaphuna okuthile akufani nokukuphatha njengemiBhalo. Le mibhalo ifakiwe lapha ukuze kubhekiselwe kuyo emlandweni nasezincwadini kuphela.",
